rows.label: qst710902_msg0001
rows.name:
Ugh! Such strength! You
all are truly remarkable!

rows.label: qst710902_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm ashamed of myself for
thinking I was the best
sniper in the Superbian army.

rows.label: qst710902_msg0003
rows.name: You all are not just strong...

rows.label: qst710902_msg0004
rows.name:
Driver and Blade... And
comrade and comrade...

rows.label: qst710902_msg0005
rows.name:
The true nature of your
strength must lie in the
strength of those bonds.

rows.label: qst710902_msg0006
rows.name:
Alright! From today, the soldier
I aim to be is not one who is
just strong by himself!

rows.label: qst710902_msg0007
rows.name:
My comrades, the people... and the
future generations of Superbians
who will be protected by them...

rows.label: qst710902_msg0008
rows.name:
I will be a soldier with a
strength that is admired and
respected by such people!

rows.label: qst710902_msg0009
rows.name:
...Thanks to you all, I feel
like I've seen the kind of
strength I should aim for.
